    <section id="albums">
        <div class="album__description--container">
            <div class="row">
                <h1 class="section__title text__purple">Here is a deeper dive into some of Sade's most revered albums
                </h1>
                <ul class="albums__list">
                    <li class="album">
                        <div class="album__wrapper">
                            <img src="./assets/diamond__life__img.jpg" alt="Diamond Life album cover"
                                class="album__img album__img-hovered">
                            <div class="album__description">
                                <h2 class="album__description--title">Diamond Life:</h2>
                                <h3 class="album__description--content">
                                    'Diamond Life' is a timeless masterpiece that marries smooth jazz, soul, and R&B,
                                    leaving an indelible mark on music. Released in 1984, the album features Sade Adu's
                                    sultry vocals paired with elegant melodies and heartfelt lyrics. 'Diamond Life' is a
                                    rich tapestry of emotions. With hits like 'Smooth Operator,' the album became a cultural 
                                    touchstone, setting thestage for Sade's enduring legacy in the world of music
                                </h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="album">
                        <div class="album__wrapper">
                            <img src="./assets/love__deluxe2.jpg" alt="Diamond Life album cover"
                                class="album__img album__img-hovered">
                            <div class="album__description">
                                <h2 class="album__description--title">Love Deluxe:</h2>
                                <h3 class="album__description--content">
                                    Sade's "Love Deluxe" album, released in 1992, is a sonic masterpiece that delves
                                    into the complexities of relationships with others and ones self. This album, known for its sensual
                                     melodies and Sade's silky vocals, is a sultry journey through the various facets of romance.
                                    Tracks like "No Ordinary Love" and "Cherish the Day" stand out as evocative
                                    expressions of passion and longing. "Love Deluxe" creates an intimate atmosphere
                                    where each note and lyric is a declaration of profound affection. It's an album that
                                    transcends time, enveloping the listener in a sensuous and unforgettable musical
                                    experience.
                                </h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="album">
                        <div class="album__wrapper">
                            <img src="./assets/lovers__rock__img.png" alt="Diamond Life album cover"
                                class="album__img album__img-hovered">
                            <div class="album__description">
                                <h2 class="album__description--title">Lovers Rock:</h2>
                                <h3 class="album__description--content">
                                    Released in 2000, "Lovers Rock" is a critically acclaimed album. Themes of love and
                                    desire are gift wrapped by Ms Adu's signature vocal excellency. The album's title
                                    track, "Lovers Rock," became a hit and exemplifies its romantic and introspective themes.
                                    With tracks like "By Your Side" and "King of Sorrow," Sade's hauntingly beautiful vocals
                                    resonate through songs exploring endearment, longing, and resilience. "Lovers Rock" is a testament to
                                    Sade's enduring musical artistry and its ability to evoke deep emotions in listeners.
                                </h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
